=== Test 1: CoalescingMergeTree Basic Tuple ===
Coalescing Basic - with FINAL:
1	(100,60,'updated')
2	(250,80,'second')
Coalescing Basic - after OPTIMIZE:
1	(100,60,'updated')
2	(250,80,'second')
=== Test 2: CoalescingMergeTree Nested Tuple ===
Coalescing Nested Tuple - with FINAL:
1	(100,(210,(300)))
2	(160,(250,(360)))
Coalescing Nested Tuple - after OPTIMIZE:
1	(100,(210,(300)))
2	(160,(250,(360)))
=== Test 3: CoalescingMergeTree Tuple before sorting key ===
Tuple before sort key - with FINAL:
1	(100,(210))
2	(160,(250))
Tuple before sort key - after OPTIMIZE:
1	(100,(210))
2	(160,(250))
